-- RBS appoints new finance chief from Credit Suisse
-- 
-- Fri Apr 04, 2014 02:15AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, April 4 (Reuters) - Royal Bank of Scotland <RBS.L> has appointed a new finance director, poaching Ewen Stevenson from Credit Suisse <CSGN.VX> where he was co-head of investment banking for Europe the Middle East and Africa.

In a statement on Friday RBS said Stevenson has been appointed Executive Director and Chief Finance Officer at the lender, starting in the new role on May 19.